  "prompt": "What is the best dictionary app for iphone?",
  "response": "The \"best\" dictionary app can vary depending on individual preferences and needs. However, some popular and highly-rated dictionary apps for iPhone include:\n\n1. **Merriam-Webster Dictionary**: Known for its comprehensive definitions and thesaurus, this app also includes voice search, word games, and a word of the day feature.\n\n2. **Oxford Dictionary of English**: Offering extensive definitions and synonyms, it is respected for its accurate and detailed explanations.\n\n3. **Dictionary.com**: Provides reliable definitions, word origins, and daily language tips, making it a favorite among users.\n\n4. **WordWeb**: A free offline English dictionary and thesaurus, known for its minimalistic design and extensive word database.\n\n5. **Wiktionary**: Derived from the popular online collaborative dictionary, it offers definitions, translations, etymologies, and more.\n\nEach of these apps has unique features, so the best choice may depend on your specific requirements, such as offline access, additional language support, ease of use, or extra learning tools.",
